{"tid":2066381,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香島中學呢間共產黨學校絕對要搞搞佢","createTime":"2020-06-16T08:46:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T09:26:50.000Z","uid":211933,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"38fbd807aa948f75b239f4944c190162f2952fea","tid":2066381,"uid":211933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:46:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=768078387062040&amp;id=219478461572330&amp;d=null&amp;vh=e\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D768078387062040%26id%3D219478461572330%26d%3Dnull%26vh%3De&d=St%2FdMm9ieZWtYGJEeV6aayIHZ%2BXcjpWsQ0IfaGt1pN0%3D&h=8b5125c3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=768078387062040&amp;id=219478461572330&amp;d=null&amp;vh=e</a><br />\n<br />\n你老母拎住香港人資源養大陸仔<br />\n收生人數40個學生得唔夠5個係香港人<br />\n<br />\n講廣東話要比班大陸學生討厭同排劑？<br />\n我屌你老母有無咁撚痴線呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上次香島學生自發罷課，幫被解雇個老師出聲<br />\n已經有d眼濕濕<br />\n<br />\n睇完中大校園呢條片，原來班學生活起水深火熱中<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家一齊諗諗可以點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n教育界比班仆街打壓到咁<br />\n點都要反cup一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請各位巴絲推上熱門<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29d6aab6ad43e1f527d23587b09210bacfda619b","tid":2066381,"uid":211933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:47:26.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e80765f10f45c6a53472ab3eb71b9428f786e87b","tid":2066381,"uid":211933,"like":0,"